<h1>\{{eui-select}}</h1>

<div class="intro">
  A reimplementation of the standard browser select with added support for error handling, and search.
</div>

<p>
  The <em>select</em> uses a popup to query the user's selection.
</p>
<p>
  The <em>select</em> makes use of list-view to hande large amounts of data without performance hiccups. To make it easy to navigate for the user search support is provided. Simply start typing while the <em>select</em> is open to filter the options.
</p>

<div class="output">
  {{eui-select placeholder='Countries' labelPath='name' valuePath='code' optionsBinding='fullCountryList'}}
</div>

<p>
  The <em>select</em> prevents the page from scrolling while it is open.
</p>


